data.description: The seller has recently made some additional improvements to the home with some additional offerings. This home has a short term rent to own option to obtain the assumable FHA loan at 3.71%. This could also be a great investment property for Air BNB because of the location. The seller has priced to sell and is including a one year home and pool warranty! Many updates have been made to the home since 2022. Come see this very nice all brick tri-level home in one of the most convenient neighborhoods in the area. A fenced saltwater pool with 17 years left on the pool liner warranty along with a new pool motor and salt cell installed within the last 18 months. You'll enjoy a large fenced back yard that's perfect for children and pets. A new city park is planned for the near future within walking distance on recently installed neighborhood sidewalks. There are four bedrooms with a fifth room for an office or storage along with plenty of living area up and downstairs. New high quality LVP flooring is less than 2 yrs old along with a new gas stove. Being close to I-75 makes it great for commuters. It has a detached out building for storage or workshop. Make an appointment today!
